## Ephemeral Replies

### Use MessageFlags for Private Responses

```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT
await interaction.reply({
  content: "This is private",
  flags: MessageFlags.Ephemeral,
});

// ❌ WRONG
await interaction.reply({
  content: "This is private",
  ephemeral: true,  // Old API, use flags instead
});
```

